  "@type": "SoftwareSourceCode",
  "identifier": "cie11cl",
  "description": "Deterministic access to the World Health Organization International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision ('ICD-11', 'CIE-11', 'MMS' linearization) in Spanish. Includes exact code lookup, error-tolerant lexical search ('Jaro-Winkler'), hierarchical navigation, cluster coding validation (post-coordination), 'ICD-10' to 'ICD-11' crosswalks with traceable certainty levels (1-5), and read-only 'SQL' over a derived 'SQLite' cache with 'FTS5'. Classification data is not bundled; users supply their own source at runtime.",
  "name": "cie11cl: ICD-11 (CIE-11) Access and ICD-10 to ICD-11 Crosswalks for Chile",
